# AMWU Brand Extension For Quarto

Provides a _brand.yml for use across projects. 

## Installing

```bash
quarto add amwu-nrc/amwu-brand
```

This will install the extension under the `_extensions` subdirectory.
If you're using version control, you will want to check in this directory.

## Using

This extension installs a [brand.yml](https://posit-dev.github.io/brand-yml/) configuration for the AMWU.

